复杂的各种应用场景。解释实时预览、代码高亮和错误调试功能的使用方法。包含自定义样式、主题配置和性能优化的技巧。","parent_id":"9248a582-d7a0-4819-954e-d5d71aad9749","order":4,"progress_status":"completed","dependent_files":"src/pages/MermaidViewer.tsx","gmt_create":"2026-07-03T11:11:05+08:00","gmt_modified":"2026-07-03T11:15:29+08:00","raw_data":"WikiEncrypted:","layer_level":1},{"id":"70dce3a5-7b23-4ad0-a851-93bacc8cbdbd","repo_id":"1c594441-ecee-4ca8-9241-c7bc9924f57b","name":"部署指南","description":"deployment","prompt":"创建全面的部署指南文档。详细说明基于Cloudflare EdgeOne的部署配置、环境变量设置和域名绑定。包含生产环境构建优化、静态资源管理和CDN配置。提供CI/CD流水线配置示例、自动化部署流程和版本管理策略。解释监控日志配置、错误追踪和性能监控方案。包含故障排查指南、常见问题解决方案和性能调优建议。为运维人员和DevOps工程师提供完整的部署参考。","order":5,"progress_status":"completed","dependent_files":"edgeone.json,DEPLOYMENT.md,.gitignore","gmt_create":"2026-07-03T11:10:51+08:00","gmt_modified":"2026-07-03T11:13:50+08:00","raw_data":"WikiEncrypted:"},{"id":"b6c263a2-ef17-4ed2-8157-af6c5de7f1eb","repo_id":"1c594441-ecee-4ca8-9241-c7bc9924f57b","name":"Base64图片处理器","description":"base64-image","prompt":"为Base64图片处理器功能创建全面文档。详细介绍图片文件转换为Base64字符串的技术原理和实现方法。说明支持的图片格式（JPEG、PNG、GIF、WebP等）、文件大小限制和压缩选项。提供图片上传、预览、转换和下载的完整工作流程。解释Canvas API在图片处理中的应用，包括尺寸调整、格式转换和质量控制。包含批量处理、错误处理和性能优化的最佳实践。","parent_id":"9248a582-d7a0-4819-954e-d5d71aad9749","order":5,"progress_status":"completed","dependent_files":"src/pages/Base64Image.tsx","gmt_create":"2026-07-03T11:11:05+08:00","gmt_modified":"2026-07-03T11:16:28+08:00","raw_data":"WikiEncrypted:","layer_level":1}],"wiki_items":[{"catalog_id":"3a941e12-920c-4caa-92d3-51eecd6f6f6c","title":"快速开始","description":"getting-started","extend":"{}","progress_status":"completed","repo_id":"1c594441-ecee-4ca8-9241-c7bc9924f57b","reference_count":0,"id":"9d215035-5f24-4816-bfdf-6df000c233b7","gmt_create":"2026-07-03T11:12:08+08:00","gmt_modified":"2026-07-03T11:12:08+08:00"},{"catalog_id":"26c32e3f-774f-420d-aa84-bdfcd76908d2","title":"项目概览","description":"project-overview","extend":"{}","progress_status":"completed","repo_id":"1c594441-ecee-4ca8-9241-c